Tested on latest OSX(10.8.2), Xcode, and Tools(Jan 2013)

sudo where needed...

Install Xcode, Xcode command line tools, macports

port install wget
port install mpfr
port install libmpc
port install gnutar
port install xz

./build-xenon-toolchain toolchain
add lines to ~/.profile

reload all terminals

xenon-ranlib /usr/local/xenon/usr/lib/libxenon.a

./build-xenon-toolchain libs (name sure it compiles FS)

and you are good to go! (hopefully)
